South African petrol and diesel prices are set for another increase at the end of May. The highest grade of inland fuel has risen from R13.76 to R14.97 in just three months.  Of course the larger your fuel bill becomes, it means you have to make amends in your budget elsewhere as everything else gets affected when fuel costs rise, especially food prices.  Global fuel prices We've listed the most expensive and cheapest fuel prices around the world:   